column2: The Finmor usually command small bands of Shearls or just use them as slaves in their communities.
Devoted to the Dark Master Be'Lakor, these fanatics worship their god blindly.
Balefiends revel in the instability they create between worlds, urging the Dark Gods to favour the Fimir once again.
